                            <p>For 24 years, Spellbound has been a place of magic, healing, and connection in the heart of our community. What began as a little shop filled with crystals and curiosities has grown into a sacred space for spiritual seekers of all ages - a home for the mystical, the magical, and the meaningful.
                                <p>We offer so much more than gifts. We offer guidance, growth, and a sense of coming home - through tarot, healing sessions, meditation, and workshops that inspire inner transformation.
                                    <p>Our shelves are lined with hand-chosen treasures: crystals, gemstone jewellery, candles, tarot decks, herbs, oils, books, incense, fairy wands and more. Every item carries intention. Every corner invites you to slow down, breathe, and remember your magic.
                                        <p>As we refresh our space and step into a new chapter, our heart remains the same:
                            
